        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Your polyps can absorb hostile magic and repurpose it to fuel your body. Whenever you succeed at a saving throw against a spell or magical effect, you gain temporary Hit Points equal to double the spell's rank, or equal to the level of the magical effect if it isn't a spell. These temporary Hit Points last until the end of your next turn.</p>"
